---
title: Pan-Fried Sea Bass and Walnut Parsley Pesto with Roast Potatoes and Tomato Rocket Salad
description: This delicious Pan-Fried Sea Bass and Walnut Parsley Pesto has been expertly designed by our chefs as a lighter option to help with a balanced lifestyle.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pan-fried-sea-bass-and-walnut-parsley-pesto-7d580ed3-368c02a3.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/pan-fried-sea-bass-and-walnut-parsley-pesto-62fa0ea2278575d03208675d-ed6b3535.pdf
course: main course
time required: 40 minutes
cuisine: Italian
nutrition:
  calories: 622 kcal
